headline.print_headline: Iran Reports Its First Death From MERS Virus
headline.main: Iran Reports Its First Death From MERS Virus

lead_paragraph: Iran has suffered its first fatality from the Middle Eastern respiratory virus, its official news agency reported Thursday, a day after the first cases in Islamic Republic were publicized.
